Package: bqq
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Quintuple Quantile Chart
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Yuhui", "Yao",
      email = "yyao17@ua.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements a Bayesian quintuple quantile charting approach
    for Phase I statistical process monitoring. Fits bayesian multi-quantile regression models 
    with interquantile shrinkage, Bayesian LASSO, and non-crossing penalties via 'Stan'. 
    Provides Bayesian quintuple quantile control charts and quantile shape statistics for various shifts.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    MASS,
    rstan (>= 2.21.0),
    stats
Suggests:
    quantreg
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
